        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> A Large or smaller creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed} in its jaws.</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Gulp: the victim is swallowed — @Damage[3d6+13[bludgeoning]] plus @Damage[3d6[fire]] per round inside (Rupture 30: dealing 30 slashing/piercing damage to the gullet from within cuts an exit — <em>the entire point of the quest</em>).</p>"
